.TH man_1_simple_shell 1 "December 2023" "1.0" "man_1_simple_shell Manual"

.SH NAME
man_1_simple_shell \- a simple shell program

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B man_1_simple_shell

.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B man_1_simple_shell
is a simple shell program that provides a basic Unix-like command line interface. It can be used in interactive mode, where commands are executed from the terminal, or in non-interactive mode where commands are read from standard input.

.SH OPTIONS
This shell does not support any command-line options.

.SH COMMANDS
The shell supports execution of basic commands available in the system.

.SH EXIT STATUS
The shell returns a status code of 0 upon successful execution of a command. Non-zero status codes indicate an error.

.SH EXAMPLES
The following demonstrates how to use the
.B man_1_simple_shell
shell:

.nf
.B $ man_1_simple_shell
.B ($) ls
.B man_1_simple_shell.1 README.md shell.c
.B ($)
.B ($) exit
.B ($)
.fi

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sh (1)

